jhave.event
Class NetworkEvent

java.lang.Object
  java.util.EventObject
      jhave.event.NetworkEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, TransactionCodes
public class NetworkEvent
extends java.util.EventObject
implements TransactionCodes

Network event. This event is used as the parameter for a network listener object. It is given a String and then parses out the transaction code by using ' ' (single space) as a delimiter and expecting the code to be the first entry in the message. It can also be given the items seperatly. It then stores this code and the message with out the code.

Version:
1.0
Author:
Chris Gaffney
